    <thetext>Description of problem:
qemu 2.6.0 drop OpenGL support.

Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
rpm -qa | grep qemu-system-x86
qemu-system-x86-2.6.0-0.1.rc1.fc24.x86_64


How reproducible:
Upgrade from qemu-2.5.0-10 to 2.6.0rc
Execute qemu with: -display gtk,gl=on


Actual results:
qemu-system-x86_64: OpenGL support is disabled
(version 2.5.0-10 works fine)

Expected results:
Qemu starts with virgl3d and starts SDL window</thetext>
